<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Your OTP Code</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #4CAF50;
        }
        .otp {
            font-size: 2em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
        <p>Your One-Time Password (OTP) is:</p>
        <div class="otp"><%= otp %></div>
        <p>This OTP is valid for <%= validity %> minutes. Please do not share it with anyone.</p>
        <p>If you did not request this OTP, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Event Management. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
